{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_ghost_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_ghost_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"圣诞快乐！","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"不知名的深海热心人士将幽灵鲨加入到交换圣诞礼物的名单中。抽中了幽灵鲨作为交换对象的铃兰，将试图在无法见面的情况下将心意制作出来。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_ghost_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["奥斯塔","铃兰","贾维","陨星","亚叶","华法琳"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_bg_bg_room_2.png","id":4},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":9},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"请进。","id":12,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"character","id":14},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":15},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":16},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","fadetime":"1","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"您好，我是干员铃兰......","id":19,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":20},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":23},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"250","times":"1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"false","id":24},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":27},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"哟，奥斯塔！咱回来了！","id":29,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#2","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"出去。","id":31,"figure":["char_346_aosta",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"jump","name":"right","power":"20","times":"1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"false","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"咿！？对不起打扰您了，我现在就离开......","id":34,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"不是说你，是让这个吵吵嚷嚷的家伙出去。","id":36,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"他接下来会说无数没有意义的和你不该听的废话，所以提早制止为好。","id":37,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"嘿嘿，什么嘛，你这么了解我啊？刚才可是我热心带着铃兰小妹妹来找你的，说要找你定做什么圣诞诅咒娃娃......","id":39,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#4","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"是“幽灵鲨娃娃”啦。","id":41,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#1","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"就是这样！这事很简单吧，奥斯塔？你最擅长这种活计了。","id":43,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"铃兰小妹妹找我们的房间花了不少时间呢，现在就把东西做好送给小妹呗。","id":44,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#5","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"......没有那么简单，你这个单细胞生物。","id":46,"figure":["char_346_aosta",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"对不起，让您困扰了......","id":48,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#4","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"......没关系，我没有直接拒绝的意思。","id":50,"figure":["char_346_aosta",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"所以，你想要委托我具体做什么？","id":51,"figure":["char_346_aosta",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_346_aosta#1","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"其实，我是在圣诞礼物定制商名单里看到了奥斯塔先生的名字。希望奥斯塔先生能帮忙制作一个玩偶作为“圣诞节派对”交换的礼物。","id":53,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_346_aosta#1","focus":"2","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"交换礼物啊。","id":55,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_346_aosta#1","focus":"1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"是的，实际上，这次的交换礼物是提前抽签分配了交换对象的。","id":57,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我抽到的赠送对象是幽灵鲨干员，所以就想着制作一只符合“幽灵鲨”气质的普通玩偶。","id":58,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"哦哦，这不是很简单的事嘛！奥斯塔，你别老是一副趾高气扬的样子皱着眉头了，还有哪里听不懂吗？","id":60,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_346_aosta#1","focus":"2","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"......这就是全部了吗，铃兰小妹？","id":62,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_346_aosta#1","focus":"1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"是的，报酬和材料的成本我会用发放的薪资来支付的！","id":64,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_346_aosta#2","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"那么，你知道规则吧。","id":66,"figure":["char_346_aosta",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"char_346_aosta#2","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"（紧张）我，我明白！","id":68,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"嗯？什么什么，为什么小铃兰这么紧张？","id":70,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"我是看心情接单的。","id":72,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"在提交接单要求的时候，我在后面标注了“每年圣诞只接受一个订单”。","id":73,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"啧啧，你是个“坏大人”角色啊。你接受的条件是什么？听着太难的玩意儿就不做？","id":75,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"......任何缝纫制品对我来说都是轻而易举。不需要特殊的源石加工技艺和材料的话，不过是一些琐碎时间就能办好的事。","id":77,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":78},{"type":"character","id":79},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","id":80},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":81},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#2","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"铃兰......小妹，你的委托......","id":83,"figure":["char_346_aosta",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"咕呜......","id":85,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#4","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"——我接了。","id":87,"figure":["char_346_aosta",3]},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":88},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#5","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"太，太好了！","id":90,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_346_aosta#4","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"（其实你的规则，就是接下第一个来找你委托的人的订单吧。）","id":92,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_346_aosta#5","focus":"2","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"（哼。）","id":94,"figure":["char_346_aosta",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"好啦，事情已经解决了，那么——","id":96,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"还没完，现在面临的问题在于“设计”本身。","id":98,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#3","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"......设计？还需要什么玩意儿？你就照着小铃兰的需求做一个出来不就好了。","id":100,"figure":["char_349_chiave",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#5","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"唉......贾维，你真该时常照照镜子，看看自己冒傻气时愚蠢的样子。","id":102,"figure":["char_346_aosta",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#3","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"谁让你说话拐弯抹角的，我是听不懂你们这种动脑子的家伙说的遮遮掩掩的话。到底是哪里出了问题？","id":104,"figure":["char_349_chiave",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"先说好，这可不是有意刁难。","id":106,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"铃兰小妹，你确实想要委托我制作幽灵鲨干员的玩偶作为礼物吧？","id":107,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#5","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"是的！","id":109,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"那么，图纸呢？","id":111,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......咦？","id":113,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"粗糙一点的手绘草图也好，详细一些的文字描述也好，或者最直接的，连这位“幽灵鲨”干员的照片，你也没有提供给我吧？","id":115,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......呜......嗯......是的。","id":117,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#3","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"啊？这么说......？","id":119,"figure":["char_349_chiave",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#5","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"所以说，贾维你这家伙也是，凡事多谨慎一些思考的话，不论是在平时生活还是危急关头都能更快发觉问题所在的。","id":121,"figure":["char_346_aosta",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#2","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"这场“圣诞交换礼物”活动的举办方式我们不感兴趣，所以没有知晓的途径。","id":123,"figure":["char_346_aosta",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"但是铃兰小妹你事先也不知道会抽到为哪个参与者准备礼物吧。","id":124,"figure":["char_346_aosta",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_346_aosta#1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"问题便是，不论是我还是贾维，至少在此之前都是没有听说过这位“幽灵鲨”干员的事迹。","id":126,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"也没有在食堂、健身房或是哪次任务行动中见过对方的。","id":127,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"你的眼光不差，找我制作的玩偶一定会是所有手工礼物中一骑绝尘的漂亮制品。","id":128,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥斯塔","text":"现在缺少的最重要的信息，是你的交换对象——那位叫幽灵鲨的干员，到底是谁？长什么样子？","id":129,"figure":["char_346_aosta",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":130},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":132},{"type":"character","id":133},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","id":134},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":135},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":136},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":137},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......唉。","id":139,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"哈哈，你也别气馁啦，小妹妹。奥斯塔只是说话直接了点，绝对没有拒绝这项委托的意思。","id":141,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"倒不如说，现在你要是想着换个人帮你制作礼物的话，他一定会拿着自己的“武器”去和其他裁缝争个高下回来，誓死完成这份委托的。","id":142,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"2","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"对不起，贾维先生，是我太着急就找上门来了。明明连礼物收件人的事情都还完全不够了解。","id":144,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"1","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"不过你们的游戏也挺奇怪的，报名者之间竟然也有完全不认识的情况。","id":146,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#1","focus":"2","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嘿嘿，这大概才是这个游戏存在的意义吧。可以增进大家的理解和关系。","id":148,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"只是，我以为只有自己不太清楚“幽灵鲨”干员的情况，没想到大家也......","id":149,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#1","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"太难得啦，这件事我竟然也帮不上忙！","id":151,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"不过这样也好，就由铃兰小妹你努力一把，去找大家问问“幽灵鲨”的情况，和各种各样的人们增进联系也不错。","id":152,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"——前提是，那不是什么不该碰的家伙。","id":153,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"这项活动的参与者应该没有那种危险的家伙吧？","id":154,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"2","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我、我认为是没有的。","id":156,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"哈哈，也对，听起来只是个普普通通的派对游戏。","id":158,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"1","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"那么先找人问问看吧，铃兰小妹！","id":160,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"罗德岛里有那么多神神秘秘的家伙在，说不定对方就是人如其名，像“幽灵”一样神神秘秘，长相可怖，声音嘶哑地徘徊在夜晚......","id":162,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"2","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"咿......！","id":164,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#4","focus":"2","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"即、即便如此，因为是交换礼物的对象，我也会努力......把礼物送给对方的！","id":166,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#1","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#4","focus":"1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"这样的劲头倒是不错。","id":168,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"小心点哦，铃兰小妹。真的遇到麻烦的情况，只要叫我或奥斯塔一声——","id":169,"figure":["char_349_chiave",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_349_chiave#4","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贾维","text":"解决这些麻烦事我们最在行了。","id":171,"figure":["char_349_chiave",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":172},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"character","id":175},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":176},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":177},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":178},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":179},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","faetime":"1","id":180},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嗯......让我想想，现在该怎么办呢......","id":182,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"贾维先生和奥斯塔先生的担心不无道理，毕竟“幽灵鲨”干员的事情，我从来没有听说过，也没有见到过她......","id":183,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"可是，这是伊芙利特邀请我参加，又是赫默小姐帮忙承办的活动，应该是不会有危险人物的。","id":184,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"只是，因为是不认识的干员，也不知道能够找谁询问......","id":185,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嗯......不能悲观！不论对方是谁，既然参与了活动，就是想要在节日期间分享快乐，体验准备礼物的努力过程和收到礼物的惊喜。","id":186,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我期待着参与各种各样的节日，获得各种各样的礼物......对方一定也是这样小心翼翼地期待着吧。","id":187,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我一定会收集到信息的。奥斯塔先生制作的玩偶总是令人赞不绝口，我也想尽我所能将让人高兴的礼物送到对方手里。","id":189,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"那么，今天就努力找找和幽灵鲨干员相关的消息吧。","id":190,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":191},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":192},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":193},{"type":"character","name":"char_219_meteo_1#1","name2":"char_empty","id":194},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_bg_bg_bridge.png","id":195},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":196},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":197},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":198},{"type":"text","text":"三十分钟后","id":199},{"type":"dialog","id":200},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":201},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","fadetime":"1","id":202},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":203},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":204},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.7","xstrength":"10","vibrato":"20","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"打......打扰您......","id":206,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":207},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.7","xstrength":"10","vibrato":"20","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"呜......请问一下......","id":209,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":210},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#4","focus":"2","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"咦？这不是铃兰吗，你怎么......","id":212,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"别着急，我会好好听你说话的，出了什么事情？","id":213,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"（平时的小铃兰可不会露出这样慌张的神情......难道说，出了什么大事？）","id":214,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#4","focus":"1","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我、我想，找一个人......陨星姐姐，您知道“幽灵鲨”干员吗？","id":216,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#5","focus":"2","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"你说......幽灵鲨......","id":218,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#5","focus":"1","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"因为、因为我问了朋友们，大家都不知道“幽灵鲨”的存在，我以为自己遇到了什么......诡异的事情。","id":220,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"呼......原来是这样。","id":222,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":223},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"没事啦，别害怕了，好孩子，你暂时没有遇到什么可怕的事。","id":226,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"“幽灵鲨”小姐的确鲜为人知，但她也是罗德岛中的一员。","id":227,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"的确......我不认为她会和你认识的朋友们有所交集。","id":228,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"但是你必须告诉我，为什么你要打听她的消息？","id":229,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我、我想送给幽灵鲨小姐一份礼物......","id":231,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#4","focus":"2","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"礼物？可是，你连对方的存在都不知道。","id":233,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"啊，我想想......是之前发过传单的，节日派对时进行的礼物交换活动之类的事情，让你要找她吗？","id":234,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#4","focus":"1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"是的，难道......陨星姐姐也要参加？","id":236,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"是啊，我也在准备给别人的礼物呢。原来如此，这样就无需紧张了。关于这位干员的消息，我还算知道一点。","id":238,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"可是，为什么到现在为止，只有陨星姐姐说自己知道幽灵鲨小姐的事情呢？","id":240,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我明明有努力地在寻找......","id":241,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"你很努力了，铃兰。","id":243,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"但是，在罗德岛中，必须隐匿自己消息的人也不在少数。","id":244,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"我会知道幽灵鲨的存在，也是因为——我们执行任务时曾一同战斗。","id":245,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"可是，陨星小姐您参加的，都是难度很高的危险任务......","id":247,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"对罗德岛来说，虽然不情愿，像我一样去做“刀刃”的人是必要的。","id":249,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"对我来说这样也比较轻松，毕竟，做那种安全的活计反而会让我变得迟钝。","id":250,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"不过，幽灵鲨这个“刀刃”，可要比我更加锋利。","id":251,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"您知道......幽灵鲨小姐是什么样的人吗？","id":253,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"我们只合作过一次。","id":255,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"她是来自深海的年轻女性。那是个无法用常识理解对方心思的存在。","id":256,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"咦......？","id":258,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"无法进行战术上的交流。拿起武器、听到指令之后，她便只会遵从那唯一的指令一直到任务完成为止。","id":260,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"幽灵鲨......小姐，她是个沉默的人吗？","id":262,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_219_meteo_1#1","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"如果一言不发叫做“沉默”的话。","id":264,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"但是，沉默不仅仅是一个现象，也是一种选择。","id":265,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"她看着那些可怖的、杀意明显的敌人，还有叫嚷着冲来的怪物们时，始终保持着那副“沉默”的样子，看不出任何情绪。","id":266,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"然后......她进行最果决的破坏，仿佛自始至终只认为自己一个人在对抗所有威胁。","id":267,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"我想，她除了知道要听从指挥官的命令以外，对周身的一切应该毫不在乎。","id":268,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"是敌是友，是活是死，从她的脸上看不到任何对周遭事物的感情波动。","id":269,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"可是，一言不发的她到底是否有“保持沉默”的自知，又是否有和他人交流的期望呢。","id":270,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"那......那么，陨星小姐，除了战场以外，幽灵鲨小姐或许还会和谁有所交集呢？","id":272,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"这可是个难题啊......不过，我想，幽灵鲨的精神状态并不适合正常的生活。","id":274,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"至少......我想象不出她普通地住在宿舍的样子。","id":275,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"你是说，或许医疗组的人更加......","id":277,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"啊！我明白了。","id":279,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"嗯哼，我刚才可没有说过什么重要的线索哦。","id":281,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#5","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嘿嘿，谢谢陨星姐姐的提醒。以后有机会，我还想听您分享更多在战场生存的故事。","id":283,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"如果争斗是不可避免的，为了保护别人迫不得已要战斗的话......我也希望，能有保护自己珍贵的朋友和家人的能力。","id":284,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_219_meteo_1#1","focus":"2","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"嗯？要给铃兰你讲述的战场故事吗......那可得让我花些时间好好准备了。","id":286,"figure":["char_219_meteo_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":288},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":290},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":291},{"type":"character","id":292},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":293},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":294},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"不过，我想，自己也很难和幽灵鲨有第二次合作行动了。","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"从那片战场离开之后，一直到回到罗德岛休整为止，她在战斗中将敌人轻巧地、利落地撕碎的过程还历历在目。","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"除非她本人脑中已然空无一物，或是比那些罪恶更加危险诡秘。","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陨星","text":"否则，怎么会对自己亲手造就的结果无动于衷呢？","id":299},{"type":"dialog","id":300},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":301},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9d/Avg_bg_bg_ri_1.png","id":302},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":303},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":305},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":306},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":307,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":308},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"嗯——请进。","id":310,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"dialog","id":311},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","fadetime":"1","id":312},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":313},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"打扰了——","id":315,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"咦？铃兰竟然主动到我的医疗室来，是想来一套“无微不至”的身体检查吗？","id":317,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"咿呀！不要做出这么可怕的假设啊，亚叶姐姐。","id":319,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"吓你而已，现在是我的休息时间，铃兰来找我玩我可是热烈欢迎。","id":321,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"所以，铃兰有什么要告诉我的事情吗？","id":322,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"实际上，我现在正在准备圣诞节要送出的交换礼物。","id":324,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"嗯嗯，嗯嗯。","id":326,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"然后，我要赠送礼物的对象是幽灵鲨小姐。","id":328,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"嗯嗯......嗯？你说幽灵鲨？","id":330,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"可是，她最近应该没有离开过医疗室，怎么会......","id":331,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"啊......果然，亚叶姐姐你知道幽灵鲨的消息。","id":333,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#5","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"太好了，我还在担心自己的推理失败了呢。","id":335,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我、我想送给幽灵鲨小姐定制的纪念玩偶，所以想知道一些幽灵鲨小姐的信息。","id":336,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"幽灵鲨的信息......吗。","id":338,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我的确协助凯尔希医生诊治过她。","id":339,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"但是，她最近的精神太不稳定，已经有一段时间没有离开过医疗室了。","id":340,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"她真的报名参加了交换礼物吗？","id":341,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我，我认为谁都有权利参加交换礼物活动。","id":343,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"不过，陨星姐姐也说，幽灵鲨小姐不会参与这种游戏，也许......也许是有人帮助幽灵鲨小姐报名的。","id":344,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"不论如何，我不能辜负这份期待。","id":345,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"这是当然，小铃兰也是一片好心吧。","id":347,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"据我猜测嘛，大概也就只有会来探望她的......咳，算了算了，没什么。","id":348,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"幽灵鲨小姐是得了很重的病，不能离开这里吗？","id":350,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"在极少数意识清醒的情形下，幽灵鲨小姐会选择出门走动一下。","id":352,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"但是，她的语言系统受到了很大的影响，与其说出让人误解的语言，更多时候只能选择沉默吧。","id":353,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"嗯......在战场上能发挥她过去肌肉记忆般从容的行动方式，也在尽兴战斗后的过分疲劳时间可以让她安心休息。","id":354,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"所以也不要太担心，幽灵鲨小姐正在以自己能够选择的生活方式活动着。","id":355,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"如果是这样的话，我想去看看幽灵鲨小姐......！","id":357,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"这个嘛......","id":359,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"果然，不行吗......","id":361,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"即使是我，平时也不能随便进入她的房间。","id":363,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我明白，小铃兰希望亲手把礼物送给对方，但是哪怕想要传达这份“心愿”，以幽灵鲨小姐现在的状况，可能也非常艰难。","id":364,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......嗯。","id":366,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"可我希望......哪怕无法见面，也能够完成这份礼物，并将这份礼物送到幽灵鲨小姐手中。","id":367,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"将圣诞礼物赠送给对方，获得礼物而高兴的心情，我想这一定是有意义的。","id":368,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"很好，很好，不愧是铃兰，要一直努力保持这份善良哦！","id":370,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"（小声）其实，只要不是过分敏感的信息，我倒不是不能给你开一次特例。","id":371,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"哼哼，谁让我是凯尔希老师信任的徒弟呢。","id":372,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"谢谢亚叶姐姐......！如果可以的话，我想收集可以用来制作纪念娃娃的幽灵鲨小姐的设计素材......","id":374,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":375},{"type":"character","id":376},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_dooropen","id":377},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":378},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":379},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","fadetime":"1","id":380},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"哟呵！","id":382,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"哎呀哎呀，这不是小铃兰吗？","id":383,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"你们在聊幽灵鲨的事？","id":384,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"啊，是华法琳医生。","id":386,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"糟糕，麻烦的人出现了......","id":388,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"我只是刚好走过门口的时候听到而已，小铃兰想要制作幽灵鲨小姐的玩偶吗？","id":390,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"这不是很可爱的想法嘛，我来帮你！","id":391,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"即便如此也掩盖不了你偷听的事实，华法琳医生。","id":393,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"其实，我可以详细告诉你她的三围和衣服材质哦......我的权限可比亚叶医生大得多。","id":395,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"可、可以详细到这个地步吗......？","id":397,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"不仅如此，我还可以帮你把娃娃转交到幽灵鲨小姐手上呢。","id":399,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"当然，代价嘛......哼哼，企鹅物流那个小贩手里卖的纪念款番茄汁......","id":400,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我、我明白了，我现在就去问问看——","id":402,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"不要使唤小孩子啊，华法琳医生！","id":404,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"啊，小铃兰！不用现在就去——","id":405,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialog","id":406},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":407},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","fadetime":"1","id":408},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":409},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":410},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","fadetime":"1","id":411},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":412},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"好了，这件事就此了结！","id":414,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"咦？什么......意思？","id":416,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"刚才不是很危险的处境吗，有关幽灵鲨的事情，我不认为让铃兰知道目前的真相是件好事。","id":418,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......她只是关心而已。她是个聪明的孩子，知道现在还有许多的事情不该了解、不必知晓。","id":420,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"一点点的好奇心就会置人于不可逆转的处境，这可是很出名的告诫。","id":422,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"不过，会是哪个热心的家伙想帮助幽灵鲨获得一些额外的善意呢——","id":423,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我猜......让铃兰来准备礼物，这也是安排好的吧。","id":425,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"唉。毕竟如果不是铃兰询问，不论是谁毫无预兆地提起幽灵鲨的消息，都是绝对危险的信号。","id":427,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"也只有小铃兰说出来这些话，能让人相信这是一份真诚的热情和关心了。","id":429,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"这件事情幽灵鲨小姐应当还不知情，节日的交换礼物......也无法及时准备了。","id":430,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"你在为小铃兰遗憾吗？","id":432,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我只是......","id":434,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"不过，刚才那句话我也不是随便说说。","id":436,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"到时候，就让小铃兰把做好的玩偶交给我，我也会想办法让幽灵鲨收下那份礼物的。","id":437,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"但是，这件事情如果让凯尔希医生知道——","id":439,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"你刚才不是说了吗，为了铃兰，连你也不惜使用一些“小小的特权”。","id":441,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"实际上，也算是为了幽灵鲨小姐吧。","id":442,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"她在收到这份礼物时会是什么反应......作为实验的一环，不也是一次有意义的尝试吗？","id":443,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"可是......我怎么觉得，这件事最后去向凯尔希医生道歉的，会是我啊！","id":445,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_171_bldsk_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"华法琳","text":"哎呀，这我可就不得而知了——","id":447,"figure":"char_171_bldsk_1"},{"type":"dialog","id":448},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":449},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":450},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":451},{"type":"character","id":452},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_bg_bg_room_2.png","id":453},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":454},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":455},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":456},{"type":"text","text":"二十日后","id":457},{"type":"dialog","id":458},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","fadetime":"2","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"呜......","id":460,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"（哈欠——）","id":462,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"已经是早上了吗。我的外套......嘿咻，好！","id":463,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"今天要去亚叶姐姐那里检查身体，去找凯尔希老师学习......啊，下午还有茶会和缝纫专家的公开课，要一直保持精神才行。","id":464,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"从现在开始努力学习缝纫，之后有没有机会像奥斯塔先生一样，能够做出受大家喜欢的礼物呢。","id":465,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#5","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嘿嘿，这一次，委托奥斯塔先生制作的玩偶，已经拜托华法琳医生在圣诞节当天转交给幽灵鲨小姐了。","id":467,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"虽然华法琳医生说，幽灵鲨小姐应该不知道自己被谁代替报名了交换礼物的活动，但是拿到礼物的幽灵鲨小姐，精神似乎变好了一些。","id":468,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","id":469},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"唉，圣诞节都已经是六天前的事了......过得实在是太开心了，到现在都还晕乎乎的。","id":470,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"希望幽灵鲨小姐也因此享受到了圣诞节日的气氛。","id":471,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"等幽灵鲨小姐好起来之后，会不会有一起聊天、聚餐的机会呢，嘿嘿......","id":472,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"好了，该拿上书包，书包......","id":473,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":474},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"咦？","id":475,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":476,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#1","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"桌上的这个礼物盒......昨天晚上，应该还没有啊？","id":478,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"难、难道是送礼物的人太多，那天圣诞老人送漏了礼物——","id":479,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......哇。","id":481,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"这是......","id":482,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"“来自深海的礼物”......","id":483,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":484},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#5","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......是八音盒！","id":486,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",4]},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":487},{"type":"dialog","id":488},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":489},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":490},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":491},{"type":"character","id":492},{"type":"image","id":493}],"characters":["奥斯塔","铃兰","贾维","陨星","亚叶","华法琳"]}